OL,3,CHiker left 'speechless' after bumping
OL,4,Cinto Kate on her Three Peaks challenge
OL,6,FCatherine, Princess of Wales, said she
OL,7,Fwanted to 'give something back' as she
OL,8,Fcompleted the Three Peaks Challenge to
OL,9,Fraise money for the hospital where she
OL,10,Freceived cancer treatment, as ITV
OL,11,FNews' Mahatir Pasha reports
OL,13,FA hiker has described being left
OL,14,F"speechless" after unexpectedly
OL,15,Fmeeting the Princess of Wales while
OL,16,Fshe was doing a Three Peaks challenge
OL,17,Ffor charity over the weekend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
