OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782742733
OL,3,CHiker left 'speechless' after bumping
OL,4,Cinto Kate on her Three Peaks challenge
OL,6,FJacky Leung was waiting for his friend
OL,7,Fafter the pair had trekked to the top
OL,8,Fof Ben Nevis, in the Scottish
OL,9,FHighlands, when Princess Kate walked
OL,10,Fpast him.
OL,12,F"When I first saw her heading up, she
OL,13,Flooked very serious, really
OL,14,Fdetermined," Leung told ITV News. But
OL,15,Fthen she smiled and waved at him, he
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782742733
OL,3,CHiker left 'speechless' after bumping
OL,4,Cinto Kate on her Three Peaks challenge
OL,6,FMr Leung said he initially didn't know
OL,7,Fhow to greet a royal and was worried
OL,8,Fabout being impolite, but Kate started
OL,9,Fthe conversation by asking if he was
OL,10,Fokay and whether he had made it to the
OL,11,Ftop yet.
OL,13,FWhen he said he had, the Princess
OL,14,Fcongratulated him and said, "Well
OL,15,Fdone."
OL,17,F"It was just mental," Leung said. "I
OL,18,Fhad never expected a scenario like
OL,19,Fthis face-to-face."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
