OL,3,CHiker left 'speechless' after bumping
OL,4,Cinto Kate on her Three Peaks challenge
OL,6,FThe Princess of Wales was completing
OL,7,Fthe Three Peaks Challenge to raise
OL,8,Fmoney for the Royal Marsden Cancer
OL,9,FCharity, the hospital where she
OL,10,Freceived cancer treatment.
OL,12,FIn a video posted over the weekend,
OL,13,Fshe said she wanted to "give something
OL,14,Fback" and "explore life beyond cancer".
OL,16,FThe future queen revealed on social
OL,17,Fmedia that she had climbed the highest
OL,18,Fmountains in Scotland, England and
OL,19,FWales ` Ben Nevis, Scafell Pike and
OL,20,FSnowdon - all within 24 hours.
OL,26,@vD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
