OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782742733
OL,3,CHiker left 'speechless' after bumping
OL,4,Cinto Kate on her Three Peaks challenge
OL,6,FKate completed the trip solo with the
OL,7,Fsupport of Mountain Rescue, trekking
OL,8,Ffor 23 miles, with a total ascent of
OL,9,Fmore than 10,000 feet.
OL,11,FMr Leung described how confused he was
OL,12,Fto see a member of the Royal Family
OL,13,Fhiking up Ben Nevis on her own without
OL,14,Fany security.
OL,16,FKitted out in full walking gear and a
OL,17,Fflat cap, Leung said many other people
OL,18,Fdidn't recognise her.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
