CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782742733
OL,3,CHiker left 'speechless' after bumping
OL,4,Cinto Kate on her Three Peaks challenge
OL,6,FIt was only when they saw the news the
OL,7,Fnext day that him and his friend had
OL,8,Frealised who they'd spotted.
OL,10,FMr Leung said he admires the Princess
OL,11,Ffor her work raising awareness of
OL,12,Fcancer and for the hospital's work,
OL,13,Fdescribing her as "sincere" and "kind".
OL,15,F"She is really a role model for
OL,16,Feveryone," he added.
OL,18,FThe Princess of Wales was diagnosed
OL,19,Fwith an unspecified form of cancer in
OL,20,FMarch 2024 and came into remission in
OL,21,FJanuary 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
